<div><head>《庾仲雍湘州記》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a.2">《初學記》引一事：<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a.3">零陵山有石燕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a.4">遇雨則飛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a.5">雨止還化為石也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a.6">卷一、《太平御覽》卷九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-1a.7">《太平御覽》引二事：<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.2">應陽縣蔡子池南有石臼，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.3">云是蔡倫造紙臼也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.4">卷五十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.5">昔秦皇欲入湘觀衡山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.6">而遇風浪溺敗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.7">至此山而免，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.8">因號為君山。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-2a.9">卷四十九。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.2">《岳陽風土記》引一事：<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.3">君山上有美酒數斗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.4">得飲之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.5">即不死為神仙。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.6">漢武帝聞之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.7">齋居七日，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.8">遣欒巴將童男女數十人來求之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.9">累得酒進御，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.10">未飲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.11">東方朔在旁竊飲之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.12">帝大怒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.13">將殺之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.14">朔曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.15">使酒有驗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.16">殺臣亦不死；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.17">無驗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.18">安用酒為？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2d1711_CHANT_001-3a.19">帝笑而釋之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
